snippet.title: Sikandar Movie REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Sikandar Salman Khan Comeback Movie Directed by AR Murugadoss with Rashmika Mandanna is totally wasted opportunity with Old Mass & Funny Emotions combined with Slow Salman Khan Action & Bigger than life poor presentation.

Sikandar Full Movie Review By Deeksha Sharma with Positives & Negatives would be shared in this Video. Bollywood Biggest Fanbase Star Salman Khan actually tried his best or Another chance would be needed for Much Awaited Comeback? Find Clear answer inside!

Sikandar is a 2025 Indian Hindi-language action thriller film directed by A. R. Murugadoss and produced by Sajid Nadiadwala. The film stars Salman Khan in the titular role, alongside Rashmika Mandanna, Sathyaraj, Kajal Aggarwal, Sharman Joshi, Prateik Babbar, Kishore, Jatin Sarna and Sanjay Kapoor. In the film, Sanjay "Sikandar" Rajkot, the king of Rajkot, becomes a target for Minister Rakesh Pradhan after killing his son. When his wife’s donated organs save three lives, Rakesh seeks revenge, forcing Sanjay to protect them.

The film was officially announced in April 2024. Principal photography commenced the following June in Mumbai and wrapped by March 2025. The film has songs composed by Pritam, background score composed by Santhosh Narayanan, cinematography handled by Tirru and editing by Vivek Harshan. With an estimated production budget of ₹200 crore, it is one of the most expensive Indian films of all time.

Sikandar was theatrically released worldwide on 30 March 2025, in standard and IMAX formats, coinciding with Eid al-Fitr.

snippet.title: Bhide ने खींचा Abdul के साथ Jetha का पैर | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah| Jetha-Bhide Ki Nok Jhonk
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

The men finally clean the premises and are relieved. The effects of strenuous work are showing and Jethalal feels tired. Meanwhile, Popatlal thanks the ladies for making them clean their respective houses. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1523
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

It is time to Unleash Your Inner Clash.

WWE Superstars arrive in Clash. Get ready.

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

© 2025 Supercell Oy. CLASH OF CLANS is a trademark of Supercell Oy. All Rights Reserved. Game includes in app purchases and random rewards.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent’s Guide:
https://supercell.com/en/parents/

#clashofclans #Clashamania

snippet.title: The Bhootnii (Official Trailer) | Sanjay D, Mouni R, Sunny S , Palak T, Nick | Sidhaant S | Deepak M
snippet.description:
Get ready for a spooky, hilarious, and mind-bending ride with The Bhootnii 👻🎬 This horror-comedy-sci-fi adventure brings together the best of chills and laughs, starring Sanjay Dutt as the fearless Ghostbuster Baba, who must face the ultimate paranormal challenge: Mouni Roy as a powerful and mysterious ghost.

Joining this epic journey are Sunny Singh, Palak Tiwari, Aasif Khan and Beyounick, bringing their comedic chops and unforgettable performances to the screen. With Baba and his team on a mission to stop the ghostly forces, prepare for a rollercoaster of supernatural thrills and gut-busting moments.

Will Baba and his quirky team defeat Bhootnii or will the ghost take over?

The Bhootnii hits theaters on 18th April 2025! 
Don’t miss this epic horror-comedy-sci-fi adventure! 🎬 

Credits : 
⭐ cast : Sanjay Dutt, Mouni Roy, Sunny Singh, Palak Tiwari, Asif Khan, BeYounik & Others
Written & Directed by : Sidhaant Sachdev
Produced by : Deepak Mukut & Sanjay Dutt
Co-Produced by : Hunar Mukut & Maanayata Dutt
Associate Producer : Johari Tailor
DOP : Santosh Thundiyil ISC
Editor : Bunty Nagi 
Screenplay & Dialogue : Vankush Arora & Sidhaant Sachdev
Production Design : Dipankar Das Gupta & Sunayana Paradkar (Teena)
Sound Design : Kunal Mehta & Parikshit Lalwani (Creative Sound Design)
BG Music :  Amar Mohile
Choreographer : Ganesh Acharya 
Executive Producer: Mehboob Ansari & Pradeep Singh
Action : Real Satish
Costume Designer- Priyanka Mundada 
Sanjay Dutt’s Costume- Anna Singh & Navin Shetty
VFX : Redifine 
VFX Supervisor - Govardhan Vigraham
Associate Director : Rishabh Rishi Kumar 
Music : ICONYK, Shabbir Ahmed, Mukund Suryawanshi (Jam8)
Casting Agency : ShoolinCast
CEO (TDM) : Gaurav Dubey
CEO & Business Head (SRE) : Shailendra Mandowara 
Digital Mrkt. Manager (SRE) : Ajay S Singh
Production Team (SRE) : Lucky Tomar, Shivam Rao 

Banner : Soham Rockstar Entertainment & Three Dimension Motion Pictures 

Don't forget to like, share, and subscribe for more updates on this spine-chilling comedy! 🎉👻

snippet.title: चैत्र नवरात्रि स्पेशल | Brahmacharini Mata Aarti | जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ | ब्रह्मचारिणी माता की आरती
snippet.description:
चैत्र नवरात्रि के दौरान ब्रह्मचारिणी माता की आरती सुनना एक पवित्र और शुभ काम माना जाता है। इससे मन की शांति, आस्था और दिव्य आशीर्वाद मिलते हैं। ब्रह्मचारिणी माता को ध्यान में रखते हुए, उनकी आरती सुनने से व्यक्ति को अपने जीवन में सफलता और सुख मिलता है।

► Album -Brahmacharini Mata Ki Aarti
► Song -Brahmacharini Mata Ki Aarti
► Singer -Angel
► Music -Kailash kumar Shrivastav
► Lyrics -Traditional
➤ Label - Vianet Media
➤ Sub Label - Ambey
➤ Parent Label - Shubham Audio Video Pvt. Ltd.
23562-DVT_VNM/16614-TDVT-23416

Brahmacharini Mata Ki Aarti Lyrics :-

जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ मईया जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
अपने भक्तजनो पे अपने भक्तजनो पे 
करती सदा दया ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ मईया जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ

अपने भक्तजनो पे अपने भक्तजनो पे 
करती सदा दया ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
दर्शन अनुपम मधुरम साधनारत रहती 
माँ साधनारत रहती 

शिवजी की आराधना शिवजी की आराधना मईया सदा करती 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
बांये हाथ कमंडल दाहिने में माला
मैया दाहिने में माला 

रूप ज्योतिर्मय अद्भुत रूप ज्योतिर्मय अद्भुत सुख देने वाला 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
देव ऋषिमुनि साधु सब गुण माँ के गाते 
सब गुण माँ के गाते 

शक्ति स्वरूपा मईया शक्ति स्वरूपा मईया सब तुझको ध्याते 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
सयम तप वैराग्य प्राणी वो पाता
है प्राणी वो पाता 

ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ को ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ को जो निशदिन ध्याता 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
नवदुर्गा में मईया दूजा तुम्हारा स्वरूप 
माँ दूजा तुम्हारा स्वरूप

श्वेत वस्त्र धारिणी माँ श्वेत वस्त्र धारिणी माँ ज्योतिर्मय तेरा रूप 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
दूजे नवरात्रे मईया जो तेरा व्रत धारे 
माँ जो तेरा व्रत धारे

करके दया जग जननी करके दया जग जननी तू उसको तारे 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
शिव प्रिय शिवा ब्रम्हाणी मईया दया कीजे 
मेरी मईया दया कीजे 

बालक है हम तेरे बालक है हम तेरे चरण शरण लीजे 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
शरण तिहारी आये ब्रम्हाणी माता 
है ब्रम्हाणी माता 

करुणा हम पे दिखाओ करुणा हम पे दिखाओ शुभफल की दाता 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ मईया जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
अपने भक्तजनो पे अपने भक्तजनो पे 

करती सदा दया ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ मईया जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
अपने भक्तजनो पे अपने भक्तजनो पे 
करती सदा दया ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ

बांये हाथ कमंडल दाहिने में माला
मैया दाहिने में माला 

रूप ज्योतिर्मय अद्भुत रूप ज्योतिर्मय अद्भुत सुख देने वाला 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
देव ऋषिमुनि साधु सब गुण माँ के गाते 
सब गुण माँ के गाते 

शक्ति स्वरूपा मईया शक्ति स्वरूपा मईया सब तुझको ध्याते 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
सयम तप वैराग्य प्राणी वो पाता
है प्राणी वो पाता 

ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ को ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ को जो निशदिन ध्याता 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
नवदुर्गा में मईया दूजा तुम्हारा स्वरूप 
माँ दूजा तुम्हारा स्वरूप

श्वेत वस्त्र धारिणी माँ श्वेत वस्त्र धारिणी माँ ज्योतिर्मय तेरा रूप 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
दूजे नवरात्रे मईया जो तेरा व्रत धारे 
माँ जो तेरा व्रत धारे

करके दया जग जननी करके दया जग जननी तू उसको तारे 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
शिव प्रिय शिवा ब्रम्हाणी मईया दया कीजे 
मेरी मईया दया कीजे 

बालक है हम तेरे बालक है हम तेरे चरण शरण लीजे 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
शरण तिहारी आये ब्रम्हाणी माता 
है ब्रम्हाणी माता 

करुणा हम पे दिखाओ करुणा हम पे दिखाओ शुभफल की दाता 
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ मईया जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
अपने भक्तजनो पे अपने भक्तजनो पे 

करती सदा दया ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
ॐ जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ मईया जय ब्रम्ह्चारिणी माँ
अपने भक्तजनो पे अपने भक्तजनो पे

Directed by AR Murugadoss, this film promises to be a high-octane entertainer set against the backdrop of intense action and emotional drama. The chemistry between the lead pair and supporting cast

The storyline, dialogues, and emotional depth

Music, cinematography, and overall impact

Final verdict – Does Sikandar live up to the Eid blockbuster expectations?

snippet.title: Durga Chalisa | श्री दुर्गा चालीसा | Sohini Mishra | Durga Bhajan | Durga Mata Bhajan | Navratri
snippet.description:
Durga Chalisa | श्री दुर्गा चालीसा | Sohini Mishra | Durga Bhajan | Durga Mata Bhajan | Navratri

🙏 श्री दुर्गा चालीसा 🙏 – A powerful and divine Durga Chalisa sung by Sohini Mishra, dedicated to Maa Durga, the supreme goddess of strength, protection, and wisdom. Chanting Durga Chalisa with devotion removes obstacles, fears, and negativity from life and brings prosperity, peace, and blessings.

🌺 Let this soulful rendition fill your heart with faith and devotion as you seek the grace of Maa Durga. 🌺

Title :- Shree Durga Chalisa
Singer :- Sohini Mishra 
Music Director :- Sohini Mishra
Lyrics :- Traditional 
Video :- Mindpro Agency

🌸 Chant "Jai Mata Di" and invoke the blessings of Maa Durga! 🌸

अपने दिन को सकारात्मक ऊर्जा से भरने के लिए सब्सक्राइब कीजिये और अपने मित्र परिवार के साथ शेर कीजिये| 
🔔 SUBSCRIBE NOW: 
https://www.youtube.com/@ShemarooBhakti

श्री दुर्गा चालीसा | Shri Durga Chalisa
॥ दोहा ॥
नमो नमो दुर्गे सुख करनी।
Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni.

नमो नमो अम्बे दुःख हरनी॥
Namo Namo Ambe Dukh Harni.

॥ चौपाई ॥
निरंकार है ज्योति तुम्हारी।
Nirankar Hai Jyoti Tumhari.

तिहूं लोक फैली उजियारी॥
Tihun Lok Phaili Ujiyari.

शशि ललाट मुख महाविशाला।
Shashi Lalat Mukh Mahavishala.

नेत्र लाल भृकुटि विकराला॥
Netra Lal Bhrikuti Vikarala.

रूप मातु को अधिक सुहावे।
Roop Matu Ko Adhik Suhave.

दरश करत जन अति सुख पावे॥
Darsh Karat Jan Ati Sukh Pave.

तुम संसार शक्ति लै कीना।
Tum Sansar Shakti Lai Keena.

पालन हेतु अन्न धन दीना॥
Palan Hetu Ann Dhan Deena.

अन्नपूर्णा हुई जग पाला।
Annapurna Hui Jag Pala.

तुम ही आदि सुन्दरी बाला॥
Tum Hi Aadi Sundari Bala.

प्रलयकाल सब नाशन हारी।
Pralay Kaal Sab Nashan Haari.

तुम गौरी शिवशंकर प्यारी॥
Tum Gauri Shivshankar Pyari.

शिव योगी तुम्हरे गुण गावें।
Shiv Yogi Tumhare Gun Gaven.

ब्रह्मा विष्णु तुम्हे नित ध्यावें॥
Brahma Vishnu Tumhe Nit Dhyaven.

रूप सरस्वती को तुम धारा।
Roop Saraswati Ko Tum Dhara.

दे सुबुद्धि ऋषि मुनिन उबारा॥
De Subuddhi Rishi Munin Ubara.

धरयो रूप नरसिंह को अम्बा।
Dharyo Roop Narsingh Ko Amba.

परगट भई फाड़कर खम्बा॥
Pargat Bhayi Fadkar Khamba.

रक्षा करि प्रह्लाद बचायो।
Raksha Kari Prahlad Bachayo.

हिरण्याक्ष को स्वर्ग पठायो॥
Hiranyaksha Ko Swarg Pathayo.

लक्ष्मी रूप धरो जग माहीं।
Lakshmi Roop Dharo Jag Mahi.

श्री नारायण अंग समाहीं॥
Shri Narayan Ang Samahi.

क्षीरसिन्धु में करत विलासा।
Ksheer Sindhu Mein Karat Vilasa.

दयासिन्धु दीजै मन आसा॥
Dayasindhu Deejai Man Aasa.

हिंगलाज में तुम्हीं भवानी।
Hinglaj Mein Tumhi Bhavani.

महिमा अमित न जात बखानी॥
Mahima Amit Na Jaat Bakhani.

मातंगी अरु धूमावती माता।
Matangi Aru Dhumavati Mata.

भुवनेश्वरी बगलामुखि माता॥
Bhuvaneshwari Baglamukhi Mata.

श्री भैरव तारा जग तारी।
Shri Bhairav Tara Jag Tari.

छिन्न भाल भव दुःख निवारी॥
Chhinn Bhal Bhav Dukh Nivari.

केहरि वाहन सोह भवानी।
Kehr Vahan Soh Bhavani.

लांगुर वीर चलत अगवानी॥
Langur Veer Chalat Agvani.

कर में खप्पर खड्ग विराजै।
Kar Mein Khappar Khadg Virajai.

जाको देख काल डर भाजै॥
Jako Dekh Kaal Dar Bhajai.

सोहै अस्त्र और त्रिशूला।
Sohai Astra Aur Trishula.

जाते उठत शत्रु हिय शूला॥
Jaate Uthat Shatru Hiy Shula.

नागार्जुन को दिया सहाई।
Nagarjun Ko Diya Sahayai.

ताहि जीति बने जगत गुराई॥
Tahi Jeet Bane Jagat Gurai.

शुम्भ निशुम्भ दानव तुम मारे।
Shumbh Nishumbh Danav Tum Maare.

रक्तबीज शंखन संहारे॥
Raktabeej Shankhan Sanhare.

महिषासुर नृप अति अभिमानी।
Mahishasur Nrip Ati Abhimani.

जेहि अघ भार मही अकुलानी॥
Jehi Agh Bhar Mahi Akulani.

रूप कराल कालिका धारा।
Roop Karal Kalika Dhara.

सेन सहित तुम तिहि संहारा॥
Sen Sahit Tum Tihi Sanhara.

परी गाढ़ संतन पर जब जब।
Pari Gaadh Santan Par Jab Jab.

भई सहाय मातु तुम तब तब॥
Bhayi Sahay Matu Tum Tab Tab.

अमरपुरी अरु बासव लोका।
Amarpuri Aru Basav Loka.

तब महिमा सब रहें अशोका॥
Tab Mahima Sab Rahen Ashoka.

ज्वाला में है ज्योति तुम्हारी।
Jwala Mein Hai Jyoti Tumhari.

तुमको सदा पूजें नरनारी॥
Tumko Sada Poojen Narnari.

प्रेम भक्ति से जो यश गावे।
Prem Bhakti Se Jo Yash Gave.

दुःख दारिद्र निकट नहिं आवे॥
Dukh Daridr Nikat Nahi Aave.

ध्यावे तुम्हें जो नर मन लाई।
Dhyave Tumhe Jo Nar Man Laai.

जनम मरन ताकौ छुटि जाई॥
Janam Maran Tako Chhuti Jaai.

जोगी सुर मुनि कहत पुकारी।
Jogi Sur Muni Kahat Pukari.

योग न हो बिन शक्ति तुम्हारी॥
Yog Na Ho Bin Shakti Tumhari.

॥ दोहा ॥
शंकर आचारज तप कीनो।
Shankar Aacharya Tap Kino.

काम अरु क्रोध जीति सब लीनो॥
Kaam Aru Krodh Jeet Sab Leeno.

निशिदिन ध्यान धरो शंकर को।
Nishidin Dhyan Dharo Shankar Ko.

काहु काल नहिं सुमिरो तुमको॥
Kahu Kaal Nahi Sumiro Tumko.

शक्ति रूप का मरम न पायो।
Shakti Roop Ka Maram Na Payo.

शक्ति गई तब मन पछितायो॥
Shakti Gayi Tab Man Pachhitayo.

॥ समापन ॥
शरणागत हुई कीर्ति बखानी।
Sharanagat Hui Kirti Bakhani.

जय जय जय जगदम्ब भवानी॥
Jai Jai Jai Jagdamba Bhavani.

🌸 जय माता दी! 🌸
Jai Mata Di!

Roop Matu Ko Adhik Suhave.

दरश करत जन अति सुख पावे॥
Darsh Karat Jan Ati Sukh Pave.

तुम संसार शक्ति लै कीना।
Tum Sansar Shakti Lai Keena.

पालन हेतु अन्न धन दीना॥
Palan Hetu Ann Dhan Deena.

अन्नपूर्णा हुई जग पाला।
Annapurna Hui Jag Pala.

तुम ही आदि सुन्दरी बाला॥
Tum Hi Aadi Sundari Bala.

प्रलयकाल सब नाशन हारी।
Pralay Kaal Sab Nashan Haari.

तुम गौरी शिवशंकर प्यारी॥
Tum Gauri Shivshankar Pyari.

शिव योगी तुम्हरे गुण गावें।
Shiv Yogi Tumhare Gun Gaven.

ब्रह्मा विष्णु तुम्हे नित ध्यावें॥
Brahma Vishnu Tumhe Nit Dhyaven.

रूप सरस्वती को तुम धारा।
Roop Saraswati Ko Tum Dhara.

दे सुबुद्धि ऋषि मुनिन उबारा॥
De Subuddhi Rishi Munin Ubara.

धरयो रूप नरसिंह को अम्बा।
Dharyo Roop Narsingh Ko Amba.

परगट भई फाड़कर खम्बा॥
Pargat Bhayi Fadkar Khamba.

रक्षा करि प्रह्लाद बचायो।
Raksha Kari Prahlad Bachayo.

हिरण्याक्ष को स्वर्ग पठायो॥
Hiranyaksha Ko Swarg Pathayo.

लक्ष्मी रूप धरो जग माहीं।
Lakshmi Roop Dharo Jag Mahi.

श्री नारायण अंग समाहीं॥
Shri Narayan Ang Samahi.

क्षीरसिन्धु में करत विलासा।
Ksheer Sindhu Mein Karat Vilasa.

दयासिन्धु दीजै मन आसा॥
Dayasindhu Deejai Man Aasa.

हिंगलाज में तुम्हीं भवानी।
Hinglaj Mein Tumhi Bhavani.

महिमा अमित न जात बखानी॥
Mahima Amit Na Jaat Bakhani.

मातंगी अरु धूमावती माता।
Matangi Aru Dhumavati Mata.

भुवनेश्वरी बगलामुखि माता॥
Bhuvaneshwari Baglamukhi Mata.

श्री भैरव तारा जग तारी।
Shri Bhairav Tara Jag Tari.

छिन्न भाल भव दुःख निवारी॥
Chhinn Bhal Bhav Dukh Nivari.

केहरि वाहन सोह भवानी।
Kehr Vahan Soh Bhavani.

लांगुर वीर चलत अगवानी॥
Langur Veer Chalat Agvani.

कर में खप्पर खड्ग विराजै।
Kar Mein Khappar Khadg Virajai.

जाको देख काल डर भाजै॥
Jako Dekh Kaal Dar Bhajai.

सोहै अस्त्र और त्रिशूला।
Sohai Astra Aur Trishula.

जाते उठत शत्रु हिय शूला॥
Jaate Uthat Shatru Hiy Shula.

नागार्जुन को दिया सहाई।
Nagarjun Ko Diya Sahayai.

ताहि जीति बने जगत गुराई॥
Tahi Jeet Bane Jagat Gurai.

शुम्भ निशुम्भ दानव तुम मारे।
Shumbh Nishumbh Danav Tum Maare.

रक्तबीज शंखन संहारे॥
Raktabeej Shankhan Sanhare.

महिषासुर नृप अति अभिमानी।
Mahishasur Nrip Ati Abhimani.

जेहि अघ भार मही अकुलानी॥
Jehi Agh Bhar Mahi Akulani.

रूप कराल कालिका धारा।
Roop Karal Kalika Dhara.

सेन सहित तुम तिहि संहारा॥
Sen Sahit Tum Tihi Sanhara.

परी गाढ़ संतन पर जब जब।
Pari Gaadh Santan Par Jab Jab.

भई सहाय मातु तुम तब तब॥
Bhayi Sahay Matu Tum Tab Tab.

अमरपुरी अरु बासव लोका।
Amarpuri Aru Basav Loka.

तब महिमा सब रहें अशोका॥
Tab Mahima Sab Rahen Ashoka.

ज्वाला में है ज्योति तुम्हारी।
Jwala Mein Hai Jyoti Tumhari.

तुमको सदा पूजें नरनारी॥
Tumko Sada Poojen Narnari.

प्रेम भक्ति से जो यश गावे।
Prem Bhakti Se Jo Yash Gave.

दुःख दारिद्र निकट नहिं आवे॥
Dukh Daridr Nikat Nahi Aave.

ध्यावे तुम्हें जो नर मन लाई।
Dhyave Tumhe Jo Nar Man Laai.

जनम मरन ताकौ छुटि जाई॥
Janam Maran Tako Chhuti Jaai.

जोगी सुर मुनि कहत पुकारी।
Jogi Sur Muni Kahat Pukari.

योग न हो बिन शक्ति तुम्हारी॥
Yog Na Ho Bin Shakti Tumhari.

॥ दोहा ॥
शंकर आचारज तप कीनो।
Shankar Aacharya Tap Kino.

काम अरु क्रोध जीति सब लीनो॥
Kaam Aru Krodh Jeet Sab Leeno.

निशिदिन ध्यान धरो शंकर को।
Nishidin Dhyan Dharo Shankar Ko.

काहु काल नहिं सुमिरो तुमको॥
Kahu Kaal Nahi Sumiro Tumko.

शक्ति रूप का मरम न पायो।
Shakti Roop Ka Maram Na Payo.

शक्ति गई तब मन पछितायो॥
Shakti Gayi Tab Man Pachhitayo.

॥ समापन ॥
शरणागत हुई कीर्ति बखानी।
Sharanagat Hui Kirti Bakhani.

जय जय जय जगदम्ब भवानी॥
Jai Jai Jai Jagdamba Bhavani.

🌸 जय माता दी! 🌸
Jai Mata Di!

snippet.title: [HINDI] realme BGIS 2025 | SEMI FINALS - WEEK 01 | Day 1
snippet.description:
Dive into the heart of the battleground with realme BGIS 2025 SEMI FINALS Week 01! Witness 32 teams clash in a relentless pursuit of glory, but the first strongest 08 will advance to the Grand LAN Finals. Get ready for non-stop action, breathtaking battles, and strategic gameplay that will keep you on the edge of your seat. snippet.description:

Aas Paas Episode 29 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 30th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Samra Bukhari

snippet.title: FULL CHICKEN DEEP FRY | Amroz Chicken Fry | Pakistan Street Food Recipe Cooking in Indian Village
snippet.description:
Watch how we deep fry a whole chicken Amroz-style, inspired by the rich flavors of Pakistan's famous street food. In this village cooking video, we prepare and marinate a full chicken with bold spices, then deep fry it until perfectly crispy and juicy. Experience the sizzling sounds, traditional techniques, and mouthwatering results as we recreate this popular dish right here in our Indian village kitchen.

Enjoy the authentic village-style cooking, the natural beauty of our surroundings, and a delicious deep-fried chicken recipe that's sure to make your mouth water.

snippet.title: Bill Gates on India, Billion-Dollar Business Opportunities, PM Modi & Children | FO335 Raj Shamani
snippet.description:
Visit Website: https://www.gatesfoundation.org/

--------------

--------------

Disclaimer: This video is intended solely for educational purposes and opinions shared by the guest are his personal views. We do not intent to defame or harm any person/ brand/ product/ country/ profession mentioned in the video. Our goal is to provide information to help audience make informed choices.

--------------

Order 'Build Don't Talk' (in Hindi) here: https://amzn.eu/d/4wZISO0

---------------

Timestamps

00:00 - Introduction
03:16 - Raj Shamani x Bill Gates begins
03:52 - Observations on India
06:40 - India: The Global Talent Capital
08:00 - Views on Inheritance
11:34 - People He’d Like to Meet Again
13:33 - Future Possibilities
16:18 - What People Misunderstand About Him
17:50 - Mistakes Made by Bill Gates
20:30 - Advice for Young People
21:42 - Problems That Money Cannot Fix
23:01 - Behaviors Everyone Should Adopt
24:32 - Perspectives on India
26:13 - Accuracy of Predictions
28:44 - Things He Fears
29:37 - Personal Fears
31:44 - Being a Maniac in His 20s
33:54 - What He Is Currently Learning
35:13 - What Young People Should Start Learning
37:20 - India’s Contribution to the Gates Foundation’s Strategies
39:19 - What People Should Think When They Hear “Bill Gates”
40:32 - Problems That Will Be Solved in the Next 5 Years
41:29 - Thanks for Listening
42:20 - Behind the Scenes
42:56 - Outro

---------------

My gear for shooting this video: 

Canon EOS 200D II 24.1MP DSLR Camera: https://amzn.to/3GuiPFK
Canon EF50MM F/1.8 STM Lens: https://amzn.to/3WZOSoi
Canon EF-S 18-55mm f/3.5-5.6: https://amzn.to/3ZpKBMy
Yunteng Aluminium Tripod (Vct-690, Black): https://amzn.to/3ItEzV0
Zoom H6 All Black (2020 Version): https://amzn.to/3irUCIf
Shure SM7B Cardioid Vocal Dynamic Microphone: https://amzn.to/3GPimiM
Shure MV7 USB Podcast Microphone: https://amzn.to/3Xjy63d
GODOX SL150II 150W LED Video Light: https://amzn.to/3XeN0aL

---------------

Today's guest, Bill Gates, the co-founder of Microsoft and one of the world’s leading philanthropists, shared his observations on India’s entrepreneurship boom, the impact of its universities, and why the country is becoming a global talent hub. From technology to philanthropy, he offers a glimpse into his journey and the principles that have shaped his life.

We discuss his philosophy on wealth and inheritance, his thoughts on AI startups if he were starting today, and the biggest misconceptions about him. Gates also talks about the challenges faced by his foundation, including scientific hurdles and global funding cuts, and why empathy is key to understanding inequalities. He highlights problems money can’t fix, such as obesity, and emphasises the importance of continuous learning.

In the last segment, he opens up about his fears, including AI, climate change, and the next pandemic. This video is about: In this video, we’ve explained how to identify adulterated watermelons and how to choose the right, sweet, and natural watermelon. Many people worry about pink or red liquid seen in cut watermelons—so, is that adulteration or something natural?

We reveal the truth behind the color—which comes from lycopene, a natural pigment and a powerful antioxidant found in watermelons. We explain how lycopene works and its health benefits.

✅ How to check if a watermelon is adulterated
✅ What farmers say about natural watermelon color
✅ How to choose sweet, juicy watermelons
✅ Signs to check before buying
✅ Amazing health benefits of watermelon

This video is especially useful during the summer season when watermelon consumption is high. Watch till the end to make sure you’re buying the best and safest watermelon for your health!

Aas Paas Episode 28 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 29th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Real Madrid 3-2 Leganés | LaLiga 2024/25
snippet.description:
Real Madrid took all three points at the Bernabéu against Leganés, who had gone into the break leading 1-2. Previously, Mbappé had put Ancelotti's side ahead by converting a Panenka-style penalty. There was no option but to turn the game around after the break, and the equaliser came almost straight from the kick-off. In the 47th minute, Bellingham, with hardly any space, worked a shot inside the box but Dmitrovic responded with a fine save. The rebound fell to Brahim, his shot was blocked by Tapia on the line, but the ball hit the crossbar and Bellingham was on hand to acrobatically slot it home. The minutes ticked by and in the 76th minute came the deserved reward of the third goal. Mbappé scored from a masterful indirect free kick from the edge of the area, the Frenchman's second consecutive brace. From then until the end, Ancelotti's men were able to hold on to their advantage and take all three points.
#RealMadridLeganés | #LaLigaHighlights

es.title: RESUMEN | Real Madrid 3-2 Leganés | LaLiga 2024/25
es.description:
El Real Madrid sumó los tres puntos en el Bernabéu frente al Leganés, que llegó al descanso ganando 1-2. Antes, Mbappé había adelantado a los de Ancelotti al convertir un penalti a lo Panenka. Había que dar la vuelta al marcador tras el paso por los vestuarios y nada más salir llegó el empate. Bellingham, sin apenas espacio, se sacó en el 47’ un disparo dentro del área que obtuvo como respuesta una gran estirada de Dmitrovic. El rechazo llegó a Brahim y su remate fue repelido por Tapia sobre la línea de gol, pero el balón golpeó en el larguero y Bellingham apareció para llevarlo a la red con un remate acrobático. Transcurrían los minutos y en el 76’ llegó el merecido premio del tercer gol. Lo firmó Mbappé en un magistral libre indirecto desde la frontal del área. Segundo doblete consecutivo del galo. De ahí hasta el final, los de Ancelotti supieron mantener la renta obtenida y sumar los tres puntos. 
#RealMadridLeganés | #LaLigaHighlights

snippet.title: Strong 7.7 magnitude earthquake rocks Myanmar and Thailand
snippet.description:
A strong 7.7 magnitude earthquake rocked the Thai capital Friday, causing buildings to sway. Germany’s GFZ center for geosciences said the midday temblor was a shallow 10 kilometers, with an epicenter in neighboring Myanmar, according to temporary reports. There were no immediate reports of damage or casualties. Read more: https://bit.ly/429iaVh

#thailand #bangkok #myanmar #earthquake

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.description:
Gokuldham Society | Gada Electronics

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: चैत्र नवरात्री स्पेशल | शैलपुत्री माता की आरती | जय शैलपुत्री माता | Shailputri Mata Ki Aarti
snippet.description:
चैत्र नवरात्रि के प्रथम दिवस के दौरान शैलपुत्री माता की आरती का विशेष महत्व है, क्योंकि वह देवी दुर्गा के पहले रूप के रूप में पूजा जाती हैं। माता शैलपुत्री की आरती में उनकी महिमा, शक्तियों और आशीर्वाद का वर्णन किया जाता है। यह आरती हमें मातेश्वरी की कृपा प्राप्त करने का अवसर देती है, जो हमें जीवन में सुख, शांति और समृद्धि की प्राप्ति कराती हैं।

► Song -Shailputri Mata Ki Aarti
► Singer -Angel
► Music -Kailash kumar Shrivastav 
► Lyrics -Traditional

अटल अनंत अगोचर अजय आनंद राशि

रिद्धि सिद्धि पा जाता जो धरता तेरा ध्यान

snippet.title: Eid vs Navratri - Hindu vs Muslim Family | India vs Pakistan Festivals | Anaysa
snippet.description:
Navratri in India and Eid in Pakistan are two vibrant festivals with unique cultural significance. Navratri, a nine-night celebration honoring Goddess Durga, features energetic dances like Garba, traditional attire, and spiritual rituals. It culminates in Dussehra, symbolizing the victory of good over evil. Eid in Pakistan marks the end of Ramadan, a month of fasting, with joyful feasts, prayers, and family gatherings. The festival highlights generosity, with charity (Zakat) playing a key role. While Navratri is a lively display of devotion through dance, Eid focuses on gratitude and unity, both celebrating the rich cultural heritage of South Asia.

While Navratri is a lively display of devotion through dance, Eid focuses on gratitude and unity, both celebrating the rich cultural heritage of South Asia.

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | HOLO LOLO | Shankuraj Konwar X Shalmali Kholgade
snippet.description:
Across cultures, resilience and wisdom are often passed down through generations, shaping how we navigate adulthood. Inspired by the famed Moran community, #HoloLolo is a soulful track performed by Assam local #shankurajkonwar, as he tells the story of the challenges of navigating adulthood along with #shalmalikholgade, who brings her unique perspective. A variety of cultural instruments - namely the toka, gogona, and siphung, play an integral role in the composition, bringing alive the sounds of Assam, elevated with supporting electronic soundscapes.

Listen to HOLO LOLO - http://umgindia.lnk.to/HoloLolo

localized.title: Coke Studio Bharat | HOLO LOLO | Shankuraj Konwar X Shalmali Kholgade
localized.description:
Across cultures, resilience and wisdom are often passed down through generations, shaping how we navigate adulthood. Inspired by the famed Moran community, #HoloLolo is a soulful track performed by Assam local #shankurajkonwar, as he tells the story of the challenges of navigating adulthood along with #shalmalikholgade, who brings her unique perspective. A variety of cultural instruments - namely the toka, gogona, and siphung, play an integral role in the composition, bringing alive the sounds of Assam, elevated with supporting electronic soundscapes.

Listen to HOLO LOLO - http://umgindia.lnk.to/HoloLolo

snippet.title: కోట్లమంది వందల్లో ఖర్చుపెట్టే స్వీట్👉ఇలా ఈజీగా చేసేయచ్చు😋Kunafa Recipe👌Ramzan Special👍Sweet Dessert
snippet.description:
Today I am going to share you most famous Kunafa recipe at home.Kunafa (or Knafeh) is a traditional Middle Eastern dessert made with fine vermicelli like pastry (kataifi), layered with a rich cheese, soaked in fragrant sugar syrup, and often topped with crushed pistachios. It has a crispy, golden-brown exterior and a soft, gooey center.There are different variations of Kunafa, some use sweet cheese, while others incorporate clotted cream or even a custard-like filling. The syrup is usually flavored with rose or orange blossom water, adding a distinctive aroma. Kunafa is popular during festive occasions, especially in Ramadan, and is best enjoyed warm for the perfect combination of crunch and melt-in-your-mouth sweetness.Do try this tasty dessert sweet recipe at home and leave your valuable feedback in comment section🤗.

localized.title: కోట్లమంది వందల్లో ఖర్చుపెట్టే స్వీట్👉ఇలా ఈజీగా చేసేయచ్చు😋Kunafa Recipe👌Ramzan Special👍Sweet Dessert
localized.description:
Today I am going to share you most famous Kunafa recipe at home.Kunafa (or Knafeh) is a traditional Middle Eastern dessert made with fine vermicelli like pastry (kataifi), layered with a rich cheese, soaked in fragrant sugar syrup, and often topped with crushed pistachios. It has a crispy, golden-brown exterior and a soft, gooey center.There are different variations of Kunafa, some use sweet cheese, while others incorporate clotted cream or even a custard-like filling. The syrup is usually flavored with rose or orange blossom water, adding a distinctive aroma. Kunafa is popular during festive occasions, especially in Ramadan, and is best enjoyed warm for the perfect combination of crunch and melt-in-your-mouth sweetness.Do try this tasty dessert sweet recipe at home and leave your valuable feedback in comment section🤗.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4357: Sawal-Jawab Ka Khel
--------------------------------------------------------
The Gokuldham men enjoy a question-and-answer game over soda. Later, Bhide is startled when he feels that Sakharam has started talking.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4357 | 28 Mar 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1090475788

snippet.title: How to make Simple UGADI rangoli designs at home || Mango kolam || Ugadi muggulu 2025
snippet.description:
How to make Simple UGADI rangoli designs at home || Mango kolam || Ugadi muggulu 2025
It is our tradition to draw kolam every day morning at the doorsteps.
There are many benefits of drawing kolam in front of the house.
It is auspicious and believes Goddess Lakshmi enters the house if kolam is drawn.
Kolam brings a lot of positive vibrations and energy to you and your home.
Draw kolam soon after you wake up and then do your prayers.
Kolam or rangoli ( रंगोली  ) is a part of Indian culture and transferred from generation to the next generation.
This ancient art form is also called as muggulu in parts of South India like Andhra Pradesh and Telangana.
People draw different creative rangoli kolam designs using kolam powder or muggu pindi which is 
actually crushed Lime stone powder available in different parts of India.
There are different types of rangoli or kolam designs like dots kolam, sikku kolam, padi kolam, Margazhi kolam.
People draw special rangoli designs for Festivals like Sankranthi (Pongal), Diwali (Deepavali), Vijaya Dashami (Dasara).
Women create deepam rangoli or kolam designs during Diwali festival time, create very big and Dhanurmasam muggulu (Margazhi) for Sankranthi or Pongal festival.
It is a belief among the people that drawing muggulu in front of the house in the early morning soon after wake brings
good fortune to them and their family.
People mix rice flour to limestone powder and prepare their own kolam powder. Muggulu can also be drawn with rice flour only.
These Beautiful and creative designs are decorated with flowers based on the occasion or festival.
